{"tid":1659118,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"大世爭鋒","createTime":"2019-10-16T19:40:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T19:52:49.000Z","uid":245782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ebf5cb1987f2d8a5b30ef6751372f795ad513f73","tid":1659118,"uid":245782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T19:40:39.000Z","msg":"屈原曰：&ldquo; 舉世皆濁我獨清，眾人皆醉我獨醒，是以見放。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n漁父曰：&ldquo;聖人不凝滯於物，而能與世推移。世人皆濁，何不淈其泥而揚其波？眾人皆醉，何不哺其糟而歠其醨？何故深思高舉，自令放為？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n屈原曰：&ldquo;吾聞之：新沐者必彈冠，新浴者必振衣，安能以身之察察，受物之汶汶者乎？寧赴湘流，葬於江魚之腹中，安能以皓皓之白，而蒙世俗之塵埃乎？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n漁父莞爾而笑，鼓枻而去。歌曰：&ldquo;滄浪之水清兮，可以濯吾纓；滄浪之水濁兮，可以濯吾足。&rdquo;遂去，不復與言。"},{"pid":"31b076ce33b3c49f5181e74548963619315e2198","tid":1659118,"uid":181581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T19:43:58.000Z","msg":"吾性汝母"},{"pid":"383b3b6022438f5baf0cbd971a796cd1cf9c6b57","tid":1659118,"uid":218575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T19:45:22.000Z","msg":"樓主中文造詣極深<br />\n仲精通天文地理 洋文 禮節<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c878088c80b914837446edcf33615afe1ed19e5a","tid":1659118,"uid":245782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"383b3b6022438f5baf0cbd971a796cd1cf9c6b57","tid":1659118,"uid":218575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T19:45:22.000Z","msg":"樓主中文造詣極深<br />\n仲精通天文地理 洋文 禮節<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T19:47:02.000Z","msg":"errrrr 無功不受祿"},{"pid":"26b312c9663cc342325e89d88b3ba37d0bf560a6","tid":1659118,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c878088c80b914837446edcf33615afe1ed19e5a","tid":1659118,"uid":245782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"383b3b6022438f5baf0cbd971a796cd1cf9c6b57","tid":1659118,"uid":218575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T19:45:22.000Z","msg":"樓主中文造詣極深<br />\n仲精通天文地理 洋文 禮節<b